title: Gradle build failing w/ Quarkus 2.16.0
body:
### Describe the bug

Upgrade to 2.16.0 fails for us with [this PR](https://github.com/projectnessie/nessie/pull/5894) (bumps Quarkus from 2.15.3 to 2.16.0). The build works fine w/ 2.15.3.

Steps to reproduce:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/projectnessie/nessie.git
cd nessie
git checkout renovate/quarkus
./gradlew jar testClasses
```

It seems that only our `:nessie-lambda` module triggers the issue - the other Quarkus image in `:nessie-quarkus` builds fine.
